 <name>Console_GetoptLong</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>A command-line arguments parser in the style of Perl's Getopt::Long</summary>
 <description>Getopt::Long allows you to specify command line arguments with
 simple descriptions and link them directly to the variable you want to store
 the result of that option.  It supports flags, mandatory and optional
 arguments, incrementing flags, and multiple values stored in arrays.  Each
 option can have one or more synonyms.</description>
